- Look. I owe you guys
an apology.

692
00:41:05.346 --> 00:41:07.679
I never should've quit.

693
00:41:07.748 --> 00:41:11.100
I don't want to be the guy
that just drives around
throwing eggs at people.

694
00:41:11.169 --> 00:41:14.153
- That was you?
- You and your friends threw
pee balloons at me.

695
00:41:14.222 --> 00:41:16.550
- I know.
- You nailed all my lawn
furniture to my roof.

696
00:41:16.574 --> 00:41:19.642
I wasn't
actually there for that.
but I'm really sorry.

697
00:41:19.710 --> 00:41:22.978
Look. that isn't who I am.
and I'm tired of it.

698
00:41:23.047 --> 00:41:25.998
This is what
I want to be doing.
with you guys.

699
00:41:26.067 --> 00:41:29.385
I used to think that this was.
like. the lamest thing on earth.

700
00:41:29.454 --> 00:41:31.604
and maybe it is.

701
00:41:31.672 --> 00:41:34.273
But we're all here
for the same reason...

702
00:41:34.342 --> 00:41:36.709
