your loving man ♪♪

723
00:42:48.065 --> 00:42:50.800
That was the greatest
moment of my life.

724
00:42:50.868 --> 00:42:54.537
- Why?
- Because I loved
what I was doing.

725
00:42:54.606 --> 00:42:58.741
Yeah. I knew before we were
halfway through with that number
that we were gonna win.

726
00:43:04.015 --> 00:43:07.516
And being a part of that.
in that moment.

727
00:43:10.488 --> 00:43:12.928
